@startuml
' 使用正交布局、矩形包风格
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

' 前端包
package "Frontend\n(React + Vite)" as FE {
  class App_ts <<component>>
  class ChatPanel_ts <<component>>
  class NeoGraph_ts <<component>>
  class LearnPanel_ts <<component>>
}

' 后端包
package "Backend\n(FastAPI)" as BE {
  package Controllers {
    class GraphController
    class AIController
    class LearningController
  }
  package Services {
    class GraphService
    class AIService
    class LearningService
  }
  package Models {
    class Concept
    class Topic
    class User
  }
}

' 数据包，用 stereotype 标明它是数据库
package "Data\n(Neo4j)" as DB {
  class GraphDB <<database>>
}

' 外部服务包，用 stereotype 标明
package "External\n(DeepSeek R1)" as AI {
  class LLM_API <<external service>>
}

' 包之间的依赖关系
FE --> BE : REST API calls
BE --> DB : Cypher queries
BE --> AI : prompt/request
AI --> BE : responses

' 后端内部到模型层的关系（示意）
BE --> Concept : operates on

@enduml
